What if you are underestimating your capabilities? You might be protesting, saying, "What of the disappointment  <u>that</u> comes from setting unrealistic goals?" However,  <u>taking</u> just a few moments to look back over your life. Chances are that you have more often been disappointed by setting targets that are too low and  <u>achieving</u> them - only to be shocked that you still didn't get what you wanted.
